package com.example.alzcare.ui.about_us

object Content {
    val aboutUsContent="At Alzcare, we are dedicated to providing innovative solutions to enhance the quality of life for individuals affected by Alzheimer's disease and their caregivers. Our team combines expertise in technology and healthcare to develop user-friendly applications that address the unique needs of our users. With features such as medication reminders, task management, memory exercises, and caregiver support, we strive to make a positive impact on the lives of those living with Alzheimer's."
}